  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The system here is quite familiar (maybe nostalgic), </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >by mixing different types of gunpowder, a new kind is created. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When gunpowder is combined with the Reloading Tool, an amount of ammunition is created </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To activate the next level you need to put in slots A, B, and C the right items. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each item has a value, or more precisely a water flow level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay sharp, some files are hidden in the dam, don't lose them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Basic Crafting</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005310/extras/472782b7c3e63543fc53ec1468144628.poster.avif?t=1773512707\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005310/extras/472782b7c3e63543fc53ec1468144628.webm?t=1773512707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005310/extras/472782b7c3e63543fc53ec1468144628.mp4?t=1773512707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005310/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1773512707\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005310/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1773512707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005310/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1773512707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Crafting Flame Grenade</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005310/extras/04f5a634da9e9c2660d65d9daa0d669f.poster.avif?t=1773512707\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005310/extras/04f5a634da9e9c2660d65d9daa0d669f.webm?t=1773512707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005310/extras/04f5a634da9e9c2660d65d9daa0d669f.mp4?t=1773512707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mixture Gunpowder with Grenade</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005310/extras/9d36cf114b1ffdbf0accb21b134a007b.poster.avif?t=1773512707\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005310/extras/9d36cf114b1ffdbf0accb21b134a007b.webm?t=1773512707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005310/extras/9d36cf114b1ffdbf0accb21b134a007b.mp4?t=1773512707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enhanced Ammo</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005310/extras/15e075350c81ce2083dcb56eeffdcf6c.poster.avif?t=1773512707\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005310/extras/15e075350c81ce2083dcb56eeffdcf6c.webm?t=1773512707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005310/extras/15e075350c81ce2083dcb56eeffdcf6c.mp4?t=1773512707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Open Tresure Box</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005310/extras/71787a1ac9bfaf5273db8f59f621c690.poster.avif?t=1773512707\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005310/extras/71787a1ac9bfaf5273db8f59f621c690.webm?t=1773512707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005310/extras/71787a1ac9bfaf5273db8f59f621c690.mp4?t=1773512707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Use your nostalgic knowledge about the mixture of gunpowder</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Collect items wisely so you don't run out of inventory space</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Some items are hidden in the Dam, you need to find them to solve the level</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The reloading tool is essential to crafting ammo, and the lockpick for unlocking</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Some types of Gunpowder when combined repeatedly times create an enhanced type of ammunition</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 40 challenging levels</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The system here is quite familiar (maybe nostalgic), </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >by mixing different types of gunpowder, a new kind is created. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When gunpowder is combined with the Reloading Tool, an amount of ammunition is created </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To activate the next level you need to put in slots A, B, and C the right items. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each item has a value, or more precisely a water flow level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay sharp, some files are hidden in the dam, don't lose them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Basic Crafting</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005310/extras/472782b7c3e63543fc53ec1468144628.poster.avif?t=1773512707\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005310/extras/472782b7c3e63543fc53ec1468144628.webm?t=1773512707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005310/extras/472782b7c3e63543fc53ec1468144628.mp4?t=1773512707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005310/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1773512707\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005310/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1773512707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005310/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1773512707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_t